Download the Wan2_1_VACE_1_3B_preview_bf16.safetensors file and put it into ComfyUI>models>diffusion_models, then select it in the "WanVideo VACE Model Select"

The rest of the models are the same as base Wan2.1. If you do not already have Wan2.1 Setup, GO TO THIS LINK AND WATCH THE VIDEO:
https://youtu.be/D4VLXF4ZNq0?si=2c3ekxuDbKbc5m-K
<- To learn how to use this click the tool tip!
If you want to change aanything except what is masked, you can use the mask inverted here. Connect it to the "mask" of Grow Mask with Blur
Use this for automasking, use mask from load image if masking manually. Just update where it says "person" with the thing you want to mask.
